				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Reflect/Bounce line is great when farming lower level zones with many casters.  I spent 72 or so points and got Bounce.  It is a lot of fun to use in places like city of mist, lower guk, nurga, dulak, et al.
<br />

<br />
It is always fun to reflect Envenomed Bolt, Ignite Blood or Ice Comet back to the caster, it takes 1.5 seconds to cast and if you see a caster run then stop to cast, you cast this spell and stand and wait, some spells get bounced for extra added fun (along with extra agro <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="Smile" border="0" /> )</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
